30
00:02:21,630 --> 00:02:22,630
What...

31
00:02:32,599 --> 00:02:33,700
Lee Soo Yeon...

32
00:02:41,050 --> 00:02:42,879
(Episode 57)

33
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:51,619
Maeng Gong Boo.

34
00:02:52,920 --> 00:02:54,089
Take good care of him.

35
00:03:03,770 --> 00:03:04,770
Yes?

36
00:03:09,640 --> 00:03:11,339
- Did you ask to see me, ma'am?
- Yes.

37
00:03:12,180 --> 00:03:14,249
You can leave work
a little early today, can't you?

38
00:03:15,010 --> 00:03:17,180
Yes, ma'am. I'll head straight
to the restaurant.

39
00:03:17,180 --> 00:03:19,420
That won't be necessary.
Just come with me.

40
00:03:36,629 --> 00:03:40,339
Kimchi is the identity
of a household, isn't it?

41
00:03:40,869 --> 00:03:43,640
The chairwoman is so fond of
my kimchi-making skills,

42
00:03:43,909 --> 00:03:45,510
so I can't turn her down,
saying I can't come...

43
00:03:45,510 --> 00:03:46,809
because I'm too busy.

44
00:03:46,809 --> 00:03:48,779
It can be so hard sometimes.

45
00:03:48,779 --> 00:03:49,779
Right.

46
00:03:49,909 --> 00:03:52,920
The chairwoman asked me
so desperately.

47
00:03:52,920 --> 00:03:55,550
That's why I came.
You know that, right?

48
00:03:55,550 --> 00:03:58,860
Yes. Of course, we do.
How could we not know?

49
00:03:59,659 --> 00:04:01,189
Funny seeing you again.

50
00:04:02,460 --> 00:04:04,930
- My gosh.
- Your husband drives her car,

51
00:04:04,930 --> 00:04:07,059
your son works at her company,

52
00:04:07,900 --> 00:04:10,129
and I guess you work
at her house as a housekeeper.

53
00:04:10,670 --> 00:04:13,300
The whole family must be involved.

54
00:04:14,610 --> 00:04:16,839
Why is this woman here?

55
00:04:17,069 --> 00:04:19,240
She's the guest that's coming today.

56
00:04:19,409 --> 00:04:20,879
- Hello, ma'am.
- Hello.

57
00:04:22,279 --> 00:04:23,580
The chairwoman...

58
00:04:24,180 --> 00:04:26,080
