59
00:04:26,080 --> 00:04:28,450
to prepare for her important guests.

60
00:04:28,890 --> 00:04:31,689
Oh, my. From what I hear,

61
00:04:31,689 --> 00:04:34,589
you're so good
at making fresh kimchi.

62
00:04:43,799 --> 00:04:48,239
My gosh, the chairwoman
must really like salty foods.

63
00:04:49,109 --> 00:04:52,940
The cooks in this house
should try to manage that.

64
00:04:54,380 --> 00:04:57,179
How could you call this salty?

65
00:04:58,380 --> 00:05:00,320
I mean, I'm just...

66
00:05:00,890 --> 00:05:03,549
I only came here
to help out a little.

67
00:05:03,549 --> 00:05:04,760
I just remembered...

68
00:05:05,289 --> 00:05:07,960
an interesting story.

69
00:05:08,589 --> 00:05:10,060
About fish.

70
00:05:10,390 --> 00:05:12,460
They're such smart creatures.

71
00:05:13,330 --> 00:05:14,330
What?

72
00:05:14,599 --> 00:05:17,770
They swim in the water
that suits them best.

73
00:05:18,500 --> 00:05:21,370
Those that need the cleanest water
live there.

74
00:05:22,010 --> 00:05:25,080
And fish that live in murky water
live where they should.

75
00:05:25,210 --> 00:05:28,880
Sometimes, I don't think
people are as smart as fish.

76
00:05:30,080 --> 00:05:31,349
They don't even know
their own place...

77
00:05:31,349 --> 00:05:33,380
and often bark up the wrong tree.

78
00:05:34,150 --> 00:05:36,890
Are you talking about me right now?

79
00:05:38,289 --> 00:05:39,289
Hey!

80
00:05:39,890 --> 00:05:41,890
Do you want to get slapped
in the face with fresh kimchi?

81
00:05:44,729 --> 00:05:46,359
How uncivilized.

82
00:05:48,099 --> 00:05:49,229
- Here.
- Yes, ma'am.

83
00:05:49,429 --> 00:05:50,969
It's top-grade Korean beef.

84
00:05:50,969 --> 00:05:52,400
Put it in the fridge.

85
00:05:52,669 --> 00:05:53,669
Yes, ma'am.

86
00:06:04,349 --> 00:06:05,880
Are you already heading out?

87
00:06:06,349 --> 00:06:08,989
You should at least
finish cooking everything.

88
00:06:10,089 --> 00:06:13,589
This will only make things harder
for your daughter, you know?

89
00:06:14,729 --> 00:06:16,989
Go ahead and act arrogantly
while you still can.

90
00:06:18,159 --> 00:06:20,029
Just wait until Min Gi gets married.

91
00:06:20,299 --> 00:06:21,400
Will you be able to handle...

92
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:22,700
