for a moment.

200
00:13:04,199 --> 00:13:05,199
What?

201
00:13:05,939 --> 00:13:07,240
Gong Boo's son?

202
00:13:08,309 --> 00:13:09,370
"Gong Boo's son?"

203
00:13:21,150 --> 00:13:24,789
So, who is your dad?

204
00:13:25,020 --> 00:13:27,319
Goodness. Stop asking him questions.

205
00:13:27,319 --> 00:13:29,159
Let the kid finish his milk.

206
00:13:31,959 --> 00:13:34,569
Gong Boo's son is here?
What do you mean?

207
00:13:37,470 --> 00:13:39,439
Hello, Grandma.

208
00:13:41,270 --> 00:13:42,270
"Grandma?"

209
00:13:42,640 --> 00:13:46,579
Yes. He's very smart and polite.

210
00:13:47,010 --> 00:13:48,079
My goodness.

211
00:13:49,709 --> 00:13:51,079
Where is Gong Boo?

212
00:13:51,520 --> 00:13:52,520
What about Hong Dan?

213
00:13:53,150 --> 00:13:57,049
Well, Gong Boo said
he'd try calling Soo Yeon and left.

214
00:13:57,150 --> 00:14:00,260
As for Hong Dan, I don't know.

215
00:14:00,620 --> 00:14:02,529
As soon as they got back
from their honeymoon,

216
00:14:02,529 --> 00:14:05,529
this kid showed up at their door.

217
00:14:08,299 --> 00:14:11,230
What? He left this kid here
and took off...

218
00:14:11,230 --> 00:14:12,370
without saying anything?

219
00:14:13,699 --> 00:14:17,439
Anyway, are we sure
that he is Gong Boo's child?

220
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:28,819
(Conclusion,
Korea DNA Testing Company)

221
00:14:28,819 --> 00:14:30,720
(Maeng Gong Boo is
the father of Maeng No Ah.)

222
00:14:34,020 --> 00:14:35,029
What is this?

223
00:14:37,659 --> 00:14:40,130
My gosh.
This is a paternity test report.

224
00:14:40,659 --> 00:14:44,000
Oh, my. She must've prepared this
in case Gong Boo denied it.

225
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:46,069
Oh, dear. What is happening?

226
00:14:47,169 --> 00:14:49,069
He can't deny this.

227
