The nurse will give you a shot.

230
00:15:08,230 --> 00:15:10,689
I'll give you
three days' worth of medicine.

231
00:15:10,689 --> 00:15:12,260
- Okay, thank you.
- No problem.

232
00:15:12,260 --> 00:15:15,470
(Han Internal Medicine Clinic)

233
00:15:16,169 --> 00:15:18,600
Hey, what did you say?

234
00:15:18,870 --> 00:15:22,140
I told you everything on the phone.
What more do you need to hear?

235
00:15:22,569 --> 00:15:24,610
That boy is your child.

236
00:15:26,279 --> 00:15:27,439
Hey, it makes no sense!

237
00:15:27,709 --> 00:15:30,010
It's been five years
since Soo Yeon and I got a divorce.

238
00:15:30,010 --> 00:15:31,880
How could this kid show up
out of nowhere?

239
00:15:31,880 --> 00:15:34,850
She found out that she was pregnant
only after you guys split up.

240
00:15:35,189 --> 00:15:37,220
Then she should've told me
right away.

241
00:15:37,350 --> 00:15:39,020
You know how Soo Yeon is.

242
00:15:39,020 --> 00:15:41,260
She didn't tell you because
you two had split up already.

243
00:15:42,130 --> 00:15:44,490
What? So, you knew?

244
00:15:45,659 --> 00:15:48,199
Well...
I only found out recently too.

245
00:15:48,199 --> 00:15:50,270
You know she had cut off all contact
with everyone from school too.

246
00:15:50,799 --> 00:15:52,169
She suddenly came to see me...

247
00:15:52,169 --> 00:15:53,970
and asked me
a bunch of questions about you.

248
00:15:55,169 --> 00:15:56,169
About me?

249
00:15:56,470 --> 00:15:58,740
Well, things like
if you were seeing someone,

250
00:15:58,740 --> 00:15:59,909
if your clinic was doing well,

251
00:15:59,909 --> 00:16:01,179
and how you were doing.

252
00:16:01,179 --> 00:16:03,610
So? You told her everything?

253
00:16:03,779 --> 00:16:06,880
Hey, Soo Yeon is my friend too,
just like you're my friend.

254
00:16:06,880 --> 00:16:08,419
I couldn't just ignore her,
you know.

255
00:16:08,720 --> 00:16:09,850
Darn you...

256
00:16:13,919 --> 00:16:15,630
Who is this?
I don't recognize this number.

257
00:16:18,429 --> 00:16:20,799
Answer it.
I think that's Soo Yeon's number.

258
00:16:25,400 --> 00:16:27,939
Hey, Lee Soo Yeon.
Where are you now?

259
00:16:27,939 --> 00:16:29,610
This is an announcement.

260
00:16:29,610 --> 00:16:32,880
The flight departing at 1:20 p.m...

261
00:16:34,179 --> 00:16:36,709
What? Are you at the airport now?

262
00:16:37,350 --> 00:16:39,279
Where are you going?
Don't go anywhere until you see me!

